                        "displayName": "Ben Kietzman",
                        "active": true,
                        "timeZone": "America/New_York"
                    },
                    "body": "It might be useful to handle this by making {{.clang-tidy-ignore}} (which is currently unreferenced) the default {{lint_exclusions}} file for {{run_clang_tidy.py}}. It could duplicate the existing lint exclusions and add any other files which should be ignored. Alternatively if lint_exclusions is sufficiently exclusive then the HeaderFilterRegex field and {{.clang-tidy-ignore}} can both be deleted.",
